<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038572" n="170r"/>
<p><lb/>Ut promissi fidem liberem Tibi significo, me <add>nudius tertius</add> salvum et incolumem
                              <lb/>hic advenisse; quod autem in primis mei officii esse puto, eo etiam ante
                              <lb/>omnia libentissime defungor, repetens nimirum debitam gratiarum
                              <lb/>actionem pro infinita beneficiorum Tuorum serie, cujus summam
                              <lb/>cum hactenus assequi non valeam, dabo operam, ut mea pariter grati
                              <lb/>animi demonstratio in nullo unquam termino subsistat. Paveo verbis
                              <lb/>pluribus confisus in voluntatis me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sinceritate<del><gap/>Ti<gap/> grat<gap/></del> Tibi (quod
    <lb/>gaudeo) satis perspecta. Ill<supplied>.</supplied><hi rend="sup">um</hi> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-104265264">Morgagnum</rs> ob pluviarum injurias
                              <lb/>nondum videre licuit, quamprimum licebit, optimam<del> ill</del> ipsi,
                              <lb/>ut jussisti, salutem Tuo nomine dicam. Accepisti, ut spero, hodie 
    <lb/>vel accipies <date when="1719-09-29">die sabbathi</date> <subst><del>litteras</del><add>expectatas</add></subst> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruo</rs> litteras, eas <add>igitur</add> qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> his jun<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ct<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sunt pro<del> me</del> me proxime me accepturum confido. Ex<subst><del>pe</del><add>isti</add></subst><pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/><subst><del>cta</del><add>ma</add></subst>tionem meam, ubicunque opus fuerit, ut tueri pergas, oro, <unclear>et</unclear>
                              <pb facs="1038573" n="170v"/>
<lb/>Fautoribus atque Promotoribus meis debitum venerationis
                              <lb/>et obseq<subst><del>ii</del><add>uii</add></subst> cultum meo nomine offeras. Salutabis etiam, si
    <lb/>placet, <add><abbr>Ill<supplied>.</supplied><hi rend="sup">mos</hi></abbr></add> <abbr>D.<hi rend="sup">nos</hi></abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118901125">Smith</rs> et <rs type="person" key="GND">West</rs>.</p> <closer><salute>Vale optime et me amare
                                  <lb/>perge.  </salute><dateline><rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3171728">Patavii</rs> <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1719-10-05">5. Octobris 1719.</date></dateline></closer>
</div>
